\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-002** [T1] Build the RenderPass framework: ordered rule stack with stable order, per-rule enable flags, per-rule quantity k, and role-filter gating. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-003** [T1] Implement R1 Metric Accent: per-beat-position velocity multiplier applied only to non-grid-locked melodic/accent voices. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-004** [T1] Implement R2 Phrase Arch (Todd/KTH): parabolic tempo + loudness arch over each phrase, modulated by section envelope. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-005** [T1] Implement R3 Agogic Accent: lengthen + emphasize notes at local contour apex or harmonic-charge peak. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-006** [T1] Implement R4 Duration Contrast: exaggerate short-vs-long by log(dur_ratio_to_median), melodic roles only, capped at ±10%. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-007** [T1] Implement R5 Final Ritardando: Friberg–Sundberg square-root tempo curve over last 20–30% of cadential phrases. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-008** [T1] Implement R6 Punctuation + Breath: lengthen terminal note at phrase boundary and insert breath silence of breath_after_ms. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-009** [T1] Implement R7 Articulation Shaping: per-note gate-time by style (legato 0.95–1.02, normal 0.7–0.85, staccato 0.3–0.5, staccatissimo 0.15–0.25) with contour adjustments. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-010** [T1] Implement R8 Microtiming Polish: per-note Gaussian jitter σ=3 ms on melodic, 1 ms on ostinato, 0 ms on grid-locked machine voices. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-001** [T1] Implement buffer-management protocol: `OnSamplerLoad(record)` allocates scsynth buffer + reads WAV; `OnSamplerFree` releases buffer; LRU eviction at 64-buffer cap. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-002** [T1] Implement `sampler_effects.scd` dedicated effects-bus SynthDef chain: long delay (1/4 to 1/2 measure), convolution reverb (FreeVerb fallback if no IR loaded), spectral freeze (PV_Freeze), comb-resonance tuned to B fundamental (61.74 Hz). (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-003** [T1] Implement `sampler_dispatch.py` that converts a `(SampleRecord, PerformanceIntent, params)` tuple into the OSC bundle (`/s_new sw_sampler ...` + buffer-pool acquire) and ships it to scsynth. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-004** [T1] Per-voice gate-controlled lifecycle: composer can `play_sampler(record, duration_sec)` for fire-and-forget OR `start_sampler(record) -> handle; stop_sampler(handle)` for sustained voices. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-005** [T1] Integrate sampler effects bus into `master_bus.py` mix slot with appropriate gain staging (peak-normalized, not RMS) and post-mix compression bypass to preserve grain transients. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-006** [T1] Implement `sample_capture_daemon.py` rolling 60-second buffers reading from `system:capture_1` (contact mic) and `system:capture_2` (room mic) via JACK. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-007** [T1] Implement interesting-moment detector: novelty (spectral flux) + transient density + RMS thresholds + duration-min/max gating. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-008** [T1] Auto-tag captured samples: arc phase, mood, presence, time-of-day, plus heuristic acoustic tags (warm if low spectral centroid, metallic if high+narrow band, transient if high transient density, etc.). (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-009** [T1] Captured samples land in `samples/contact/` or `samples/room/` as 24-bit 48 kHz WAV with metadata-tagged filename and an entry in `index.sqlite`. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-010** [T1] Implement self-quotation loop: when a song completes with arc-payoff > threshold AND clicks=0, sample a 4-second window of `SuperCollider:out_1` for the next session. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\